1 -

cd ~
wget https://sourceforge.net/projects/zsh/files/latest/download -O zsh.tar.xz

----------------------------------

2 -

tar -xf zsh.tar.xz
cd zsh-*

-----------------------------------

3 -

./configure --prefix=$HOME/.local
make
make install


--------------------------------

4 -

Abre o teu ~/.bashrc e adiciona essa linha no final:

export PATH="$HOME/.local/bin:$PATH"

---------------------------------

5 -

source ~/.bashrc


--------------------

